echo music:
This project was born from my personal frustration. Like many music lovers, I found myself constantly running into paywalls—basic features like lyrics, playlists, and quality playback were hidden behind subscriptions. I wanted freedom. I wanted control over how I listened to music. So I stopped waiting for someone else to build it, and I built it myself.

URL: https://github.com/ashxorg/echo-music
